com.hazelcast.spi.impl.operationservice.impl.responses

Class BackupAckResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.spi.impl.operationservice.impl.responses.Response
      • com.hazelcast.spi.impl.operationservice.impl.responses.BackupAckResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSerializable, IdentifiedDataSerializable

    public final class BackupAckResponse
extends Response
    The {Response} for a BackupOperation. So when a operation like Map.put is done, backup operations are send to the backup partitions. For the initial Map.put to complete, the NormalResponse needs to return, but also the BackupAckResponse to make sure that the change is written to the expected number of backups.
